<title type="html"><![CDATA[9/2(Thu)Know your enemy:Rise of the Roaches/7 Ways:Home Cooking Beats Ordering and take out(host:Larry)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=538&amp;p=561#p561"><![CDATA[
Place: On-Line Zoom Meeting <br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ... 09#success<br />會議 ID: 929 8726 6213<br />密碼: 112233 <br />Agenda:<br />07:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks <br />07:05-7:40 pm Session 1 Group Discussion<br />07:40-8:00 pm Presentation (At least two members of each table are invited, 2 mins / each member)<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40 pm Session 2 discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Presentation<br />Session 1 <br />Know your enemy: Rise of the Roaches<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://blog.rentokil.co.za/know-your-enemy-cockroaches">https://blog.rentokil.co.za/know-your-enemy-cockroaches</a><!-- m --> <br /><br />1. Do you have any problems with cockroaches or ants or any other insects in your house? What do you usually do with them and how effective is it? Can you completely eradicate them? <br />2. Why are so many people afraid of cockroaches? Are you scared of it?  How scared are you? Can you share your experience? <br />3. We know cockroaches are one of the most difficult pests to eradicate, so if the house is kept clean all the time, will there be no cockroaches? Is this true? Why? <br />4. Do you think it’s wrong to be afraid of cockroaches if one is a man? We know some phobias are genetic, can we overcome them and why? <br /><br />Session 2 <br />7 Ways:  Home Cooking Beats Ordering and<br />Takeout <br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.healthline.com/health/food-nutrition/home-cooking-versus-takeout">https://www.healthline.com/health/food- ... us-takeout</a><!-- m --> <br /><br />1. Cooking at home generally can save a lot of time and money, and is more hygienic and healthy, is this true and why? Please share your experience. <br />2. If you have time, will you cook at home or eat out? Why? <br />3. Can you cook and enjoy it? Do you think preparing meals for your family is an easy job for you or not? Why? <br />4. Do you bring your lunch on the day at work or just eat out? What are pros and cons? <br />5. Do you think your husband should learn how to cook and why?<br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=89">AndrewWang</a> — Mon Aug 30, 2021 11:07 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
